<li> So sorry for your loss; may cherished memories bring you solace.</li>
<li> I'm here for you, whatever you need, please don’t hesitate to reach out.</li>
<li> Sending you strength and love during this incredibly sad time.</li>
<li> Thinking of you and remembering the good times you shared with [deceased's name].</li>
<li> I'll always cherish the memories of [deceased's name].  They were a wonderful person.</li>
<li> [deceased's name] will be deeply missed.  My thoughts are with you.</li>
<li> My heart is with you as you grieve the loss of your dear friend.</li>
<li> You are not alone in your grief.  Please lean on me if you need anything.</li>
<li> Remembering [deceased's name]'s kindness and generosity;  They'll be missed by many.</li>
